{"tid":908462,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以不失霸氣咁搭小巴","createTime":"2018-11-19T14:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T15:31:06.000Z","uid":43342,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"127a993f7de6406dde50baca5db38a8718c8481b","tid":908462,"uid":43342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:46:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n本人一直都有個問題，就係毒到唔敢搭小巴。因為小巴司機太霸氣，每次俾佢大聲一凶，都嚇到我菊花一緊。知道邊度落又唔知幾時叫，叫左又唔知佢聽唔聽到。每次搭小巴都來回地獄又折返人間咁。"},{"pid":"3ae87a2fc482d110ccef9c28b5f0b8c7d354bfbe","tid":908462,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"尾站先落車"},{"pid":"3e7f45375b36afa114c1e10f4c223ef40a476ca1","tid":908462,"uid":43342,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ae87a2fc482d110ccef9c28b5f0b8c7d354bfbe","tid":908462,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"尾站先落車"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T14:49:03.000Z","msg":"我淨係搭到喺尾站落車嘅小巴"},{"pid":"454a239f8879ed9bdf3211e7c2738a3cbe3d1b36","tid":908462,"uid":198362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:25:23.000Z","msg":"下次試下講：「師兄，麻煩你前面巴士站停一停。」<br />\n<br />\n通常司機會變得好有禮貌，與此同時你會發現會有幾位乘客開始扣上安全帶"},{"pid":"fda025a252fc4fd38617ece1f8bec5b711ef1bba","tid":908462,"uid":149879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"一上車就嗌有落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25087a23396028b7084a57e785bb63146bed1dd8","tid":908462,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"禁鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}